episodes.title: Louis Theroux in New York City talking My Scientology Movie with Brad Blanks
episodes.description:
Back in 2001 while sitting on a couch in London awaiting the call up to New York City radio I watched a lot of Louis Theroux and his 2nd show "When Louis Met....." From this video you can tell I was a dash excited to meet one of the greatly understated (and very funny!) documentarians walking around today. His new movie is called "My Scientology Movie" and it's a wild adventure into that very controlled world. Hope you enjoy the chat......
